Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"score\": 0.9999999548776951, \"rank\": 4.497728514666631e-08, \"text\": \"UVA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Virginia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"itsofficial Olympic\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"14 athletes\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"non\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See the full list of UVA-affiliated athletes on the Team USA roster for the 2024 Paris Olympics below:Will Coleman - EquestrianDanielle Collins - TennisSkylar Dahl - Para-RowingKate Douglass - SwimmingThomas Heilman - Swimming (UVA swim & dive commit)Aaron Keith - Para-Cycling *UVA School of Medicine*Paige Madden - SwimmingEmma Navarro - Tennis *not a graduate*Matt Simpson - Goal Ball (Paralympics) *UVA Law*Emily Sonnett - SoccerAlex Walsh - SwimmingGretchen Walsh - Swimming (current undergrad)Emma Weber - Swimming (current undergrad)Bridget Williams - Track & Field Included in that list are seven multi-time Olympians: Will Coleman (2012), Kate Douglass (2020), Aaron Keith (2020), Paige Madden (2020), Matt Simpson (2016 & 2020), Emily Sonnett (2020), and Alex Walsh (2020), six of whom are already Olympic medalists: Kate Douglass (bronze in 200m IM), Aaron Keith (silver in Para-Cycling), Paige Madden (silver in 4x200m free relay), Matt Simpson (silver in Goal Ball), Emily Sonnett (bronze in women's soccer), and Alex Walsh (silver in 200m IM).\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketb